ipax-cli
========

This project contains code derived from third-party sources listed below.
A license has been requested from each author and is pending.


1. IPAX 2 — Santiago Bustelo
   Website : https://www.bustelo.com.ar/
   Source  : https://icograma.com/index.php
   Status  : License requested — pending author approval

   The following files are derived works of IPAX 2 r.20260517:
     ipax-core.js          — scoring orchestrator (ported to Node.js ESM)
     ipax-color-math.js    — OKLCh color space conversions
     ipax-apca-bridge.js   — APCA Lc calculation and font sizing
     ipax-ergonomics.js    — perceptual penalty and reward engine
     ipax-dictionary.js    — penalty/reward data and scientific references

   Adaptation: IIFE browser modules converted to ES module exports.
   The scoring algorithms, physiological models, and penalty/reward data
   are reproduced with the intent to credit and obtain permission.


